&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quantify Client Impact: Ensure customers can clearly articulate and attribute specific business outcomes (savings, lift, etc.) to delivered initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Standardize Frameworks: Implement and scale a repeatable Value Realization framework across your assigned portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
