&lt;h3&gt;CLOUD APPLICATION ENGINEER&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What experience should you have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of professional web application development experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong command of TypeScript and either Go or Python with full-stack development experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Google Cloud Platform, specifically Load Balancing and web architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience operating Cloud Run applications in production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with Git workflows and agile development processes (SDLC).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred: &lt;/strong&gt;Professional Cloud Developer certification or experience in client-facing consulting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What you’ll be doing in this role:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and implement web applications using TypeScript (Svelte), Go, and Python (FastAPI).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and optimize PostgreSQL database schemas to ensure performance and data integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage application deployments on GCP using Cloud Run and Cloud SQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop user-friendly interfaces using modern frameworks like Svelte.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with data science teams to integrate AI models into production APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What you&#39;ll need to accomplish in your first year:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successfully deploy and maintain high-availability cloud applications for client projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently deliver clean, secure, and performant code that meets team standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become a key contributor to the technical integration of AI-driven features into web interfaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
