&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;GCP Professional certifications (Cloud Architect, Data Engineer, or equivalent).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Experience with containerized workloads: GKE, Cloud Run, or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Familiarity with data migration tooling: Database Migration Service, Datastream, Transfer Service.&lt;/li&gt;
